{"tid":1291841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會選舉引入「確認書」制度 7月10前截，無人遊行？","createTime":"2019-07-07T05:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T14:45:50.000Z","uid":260428,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"78182d972bc31cdc29e8aeddd0d77bfc77635b44","tid":1291841,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"選舉管理委員會原訂今晚舉行區議會選舉活動建議指引公眾諮詢會，但經風險評估後，基於「公眾安全和保安考慮」決定取消。 <br />\n<br />\n政府的新聞稿指，選管會公眾諮詢大會，原定今晚 7 時至 9 時在鰂魚涌舉行，由於要考慮場內所有參與者的安全，經風險評估，決定取消今晚的大會。選管會建議指引的公眾諮詢，由 6 月 11 日開始，諮詢期到 7 月 10 日結束，為期三十日，當局指巿民可提供書面意見。<br />\n<br />\n選管會今次提出修改「區議會選舉活動建議指引」，其中一項修訂包括在區議會選舉引入「確認書」制度。公民黨昨日在 fb 發文，指「確認書殺入區議會選舉 DQ參選人更方便」，呼籲公眾關注今晚的諮詢會，「做個好公民，記得積極去發表意見！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n選管會暫時未有提及會否改期重辦公眾諮詢大會，如就建議指引內容有書面意見，可以從三個方式表達：郵寄（香港灣仔港灣道二十五號海港中心十樓選管會秘書處）、傳真（2511 1682）及電郵（eacenq@eac.hk）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無公眾諮詢<br />\n大家有無寫信格式建議"},{"pid":"b906ab1f305d62000a568760aec8adb64f94b25e","tid":1291841,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"正經野吖，唔好只掛住家人x"},{"pid":"fc9d16edd10a7936287206c360372338db23d76a","tid":1291841,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:16:06.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"36e3a93528288ea941afee88fc0e9e9f92d5514d","tid":1291841,"uid":260428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"debd40f7c8339becc273d1db7cb06ba137c4d532","tid":1291841,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cb4085e29daa224e556965c52d71e61fe9cfb3f","tid":1291841,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ab99b1108f23324069fe8dc11db1d24a5d67aaa","tid":1291841,"uid":44415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da274b50be0d62867aaa617384f46f9c56393d5f","tid":1291841,"uid":189919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:19:35.000Z","msg":"[3000萬個火急] 一人一信反對區議會DQ機制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284662</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55ea596257336e9771a09a9d98eb6b4b56939d1e","tid":1291841,"uid":189919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da274b50be0d62867aaa617384f46f9c56393d5f","tid":1291841,"uid":189919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:19:35.000Z","msg":"[3000萬個火急] 一人一信反對區議會DQ機制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284662</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"有哂格式,<br />\n只要落個名同加幾句意見就得<br />\n快d入去send信"},{"pid":"7f1d0fe987ef233aa781549ac5656429170b0d4c","tid":1291841,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"唔理你係和理非定勇武都入一入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https:/